		<title>VMworld: Day 4 &#8211; The &#034;Unofficial&#034; Summary Guide</title>
		<link>http://www.ericvb.com/archives/vmworld-day-4-the-unofficial-summary-guide</link>
					<comments>http://www.ericvb.com/archives/vmworld-day-4-the-unofficial-summary-guide#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Vanberge]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2013 14:17:00 +0000</pubDate>
